snippet.title: Johnny Depp Reveals Hollywood is Protecting Amber Heard
snippet.description:
►Johnny Depp Reveals Hollywood is Protecting Amber Heard
The studio announced on Friday that “Johnny Depp will leave the Fantastic Beasts franchise.” “We appreciate Johnny's contributions to the films thus far. Gellert Grindelwald will be recast in Fantastic Beasts 3, which is now in development. The film will be released in theatres around the world in the summer of 2022′′.
